Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.17,0:03:59.30,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Parabéns, Kunato.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.30,0:04:01.05,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Foi em um piscar de olhos.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.26,0:04:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hã? Não é dia de comer hoje?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.43,0:04:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles estão todos comendo no Festival da Gravidade.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.47,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,O Festival da Gravidade?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.01,0:04:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, certo.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnLEHN236\fs60\blur0.5\bord3\1c&H4E7B99&\3c&H4E7B99&\pos(378,143)}Festival da Gravidade
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnLEHN236\fs25\blur0.5\1c&H182F4C&\pos(378,96)}Lanternas de Higgs
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnLEHN236\fs30\blur0.5\1c&H182F4C&\pos(378,116)}Uma tradição com mais de 800 anos
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.73,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnLEHN236\fs60\blur0.5\1c&H182F4C&\pos(378,143)}Festival da Gravidade
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Com seus ferimentos, você está fora de disputa pelo troféu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.19,0:04:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu realmente acho que está tudo bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Vá em frente, então.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.73,0:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tem muita comida ótima lá.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnLEHN236\fs60\blur0.5\bord3\1c&H4E7B99&\3c&H4E7B99&\pos(335,160)}Festival da Gravidade
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnLEHN236\fs25\blur0.5\1c&H182F4C&\pos(335,113)}Lanternas Hyggs
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnLEHN236\fs30\blur0.5\1c&H182F4C&\pos(335,133)}Uma tradição com mais de 800 anos
Dialogue: 2,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.20,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnLEHN236\fs60\blur0.5\1c&H182F4C&\pos(335,160)}Festival da Gravidade
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.65,0:04:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sério?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.49,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.20,0:04:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ok, tchau!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.02,0:04:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos assistir mais uma vez à partida crucial de Nin Kunato.
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Hazama Kaoru]
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Kunato Norio]
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Hazama Kaoru]
Dialogue: 2,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Kunato Norio]
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele é muito bom.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Você precisa aumentar o nível, Akai.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.28,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,É bom ver um talento novo por aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Próximo combate: Tsuruuchi contra Aoki, em dez minutos.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.86,0:05:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Certo.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa sorte.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.12,0:05:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuruuchi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.66,0:05:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos tente vencer.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.33,0:05:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Samari...]
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.71,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Se eu vencer isso, você vai fotossintetizar comigo?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Tsuruuchi...]
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ataque!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Vencedor: Aoki!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Tsuruuchi Kouichi]
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Aoki Hakushu]
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Tsuruuchi Kouichi]
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.18,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Aoki Hakushu]
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki está em condições incríveis de novo!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Tsuruuchi]
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Kouichi]
Dialogue: 2,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.60,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fnZekton\c&HFFFFFF&\b1\fs20\fax0.17\blur0.5\frz351\pos(636,574)}Membro da Unidade Sul
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.81,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele derrotou o formidável Tsuruuchi!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyama[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Você viu o Nagate?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.35,0:05:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele foi ao festival sozinho.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.02,0:05:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, entendi. Obrigada!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.73,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos descobrir quem é mais digno de empunhar um Kabizashi!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.41,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,O Akai {**-san} é muito incrível.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mas o Aoki também {**-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,O Midorikawa {**-san} também está indo muito bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.08,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, o Kunato vai ganhar este ano.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.62,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Kunato Development construiu o Tipo 18 principal atual.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,524,1,\3c&H20221B&\4c&H211E0D&)}Eles fizeram melhorias substanciais no piloto automático,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.17,0:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mas ações complicadas ainda exigem uma pessoa real.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.76,0:06:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O Tipo 17 do século passado aparentemente depende muito mais da habilidade do piloto.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(861,0)\c&H6E8195&\fnAveria Serif\frx3\fs23\blur0.5\bord0.6\3c&H677F8D&\pos(648,220)\t(5575,6075,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Tipo 17 Garde Versão Shiratsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Tsugumori]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(861,0)\c&H6E8195&\fnAveria Serif\frx3\fs26\blur0.5\bord0.6\3c&H677F8D&\fscx92\fscy100\pos(644,536)\t(5575,6075,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Este chassi especial da versão Shiratsuki foi usado no final da Quarta Guerra de Defesa contra Gaunas
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(861,0)\c&HABCFEC&\shad1.4\frx3\fnAveria Serif\fs23\blur1\4c&H96BFE7&\pos(648,220)\t(5575,6075,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Tipo 17 Garde Versão Shiratsuki
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Tsugumori]
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(861,0)\c&HABCFEC&\shad1.4\frx3\fnAveria Serif\fs26\blur1\4c&H96BFE7&\fscx92\fscy100\pos(644,536)\t(5575,6075,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Este chassi especial da versão Shiratsuki foi usado no final da Quarta Guerra de Defesa contra Gaunas
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(861,0)\c&HABCFEC&\xshad-1\yshad1\frx3\fnAveria Serif\fs23\blur1\3c&H677F8D&\4c&H5B6C80&\pos(648,220)\t(5575,6075,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Tipo 17 Garde Versão Shiratsuki
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Tsugumori]
Dialogue: 2,0:06:16.02,0:06:22.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(861,0)\c&HABCFEC&\xshad-1\yshad1\frx3\fnAveria Serif\fs26\blur1\3c&H677F8D&\4c&H5B6C80&\fscx92\fscy100\pos(644,536)\t(5575,6075,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Este chassi especial da versão Shiratsuki foi usado no final da Quarta Guerra de Defesa contra Gaunas
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.85,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tanikaze Nagate foi capaz de lutar de igual para igual contra um Gauna e sobreviver.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.11,Sign,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Começar!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato salta direto para dentro!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.07,0:06:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Se Tanikaze{**-san} participasse deste torneio...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.41,0:06:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Finalmente te achei!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Você é Tanikaze Nagate{**-san}, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Olá! Eu sou Yuhata.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa Yuhata!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.12,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,É um prazer te conhecer pessoalmente!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei, Yuhata! Estamos no\Nmeio de algo aqui!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.92,0:06:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Irmão{*Onii-chan}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.34,0:06:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Não preste atenção nela.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.93,0:06:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0.]
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Akai Mochikuni.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.35,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um piloto completo de Garde.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.47,0:06:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Este é Aoki e Midorikawa, meus companheiros de esquadrão.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.68,0:07:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx100}...{\r}E este é—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sou Momose.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.39,0:07:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Prazer em conhecê-los.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.27,0:07:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Como posso ajudar?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.69,0:07:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu só queria dar uma olhada no homem que enfrentou um Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.53,0:07:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Como foi?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.24,0:07:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você achou do seu primeiro Gauna?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.91,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Não muito na época...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.70,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu fiz o mesmo que faria no Simulador de RV.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.63,0:07:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Como de costume, né?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.13,0:07:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Você desviou dos braços placentários dele por instinto?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.55,0:07:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não teve medo?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.22,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles devem ter estado tão perto de você.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.47,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Tanikaze{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.64,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Não, não.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A tala é o problema.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.48,0:07:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Já sarou,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.78,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,mas eles não vão deixar eu tirar.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Meu estômago está roncando.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.74,0:07:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Você {\i1}disse{\i0} que estava com fome.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.04,0:08:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Acho que você realmente não consegue fotossintetizar,\Ncomo os rumores diziam.{Guess the rumors had it right\Nand you really can't photosynthesize.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.21,0:08:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.54,0:08:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece que você está com fome,\Nentão vamos continuar {our discussion }outra vez.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ok.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.92,0:08:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ter mais perguntas,\Npara você então.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou ajudar no que puder.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Até mais.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.01,0:08:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos, Yuhata.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.97,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que você não me deixa em paz, {*}Irmão{*Onii-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Você sabe o que eu tive que fazer para encontrá-lo?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Não foi você quem estava no nosso caminho?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.94,0:08:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo aqui, de qualquer forma?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.69,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,O único motivo pelo qual todos os estagiários, exceto um, conseguiram voltar do encontro com os Gauna
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,é que Tsugumori parou isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Como você sabe disso?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.08,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Esse material não está disponível para os alunos!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.29,0:08:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho uma noção do que aconteceu com base no\Nque tirei dos registros de reparo dos Garde.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.75,0:08:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, uma "noção".
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem, é por isso que eu quero\Nconversar com ele e saber mais!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.55,0:08:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Meu Deus.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.18,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Como Tanikaze{**-san} se sairá?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.19,0:09:08.10,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Que ataque terrível de Kunato!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.10,0:09:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Não está nada mal.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.86,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Não foi o suficiente!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.36,0:09:10.98,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{announcer}Isso está muito desequilibrado!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.98,0:09:12.98,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{announcer}Faltam trinta segundos!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.23,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sou melhor que você!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.44,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Vamos para prorrogação?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.44,0:09:16.45,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Um deles conseguirá vencer até então?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.45,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.03,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Passou...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.78,0:09:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,por cima do ombro dele.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.17,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ataque!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Acabou!{TLC}{I've watched over 20 animes and it sounds good to me}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.21,0:09:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Vencedor: Akai!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Akai Mochikuni é o vencedor!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.88,0:09:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele desviou dos brilhantes ataques de Kunato e venceu em um único golpe!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.97,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{\i1}Aqueles movimentos...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ele assistiu à batalha de Tanikaze{**-san} contra os Gauna?{\i0}
Dialogue: 2,0:09:54.90,0:09:59.03,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Teppanyaki]
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.49,0:10:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, um desses.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.32,0:10:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Sem problemas. Faz quinhentos ienes.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.37,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.96,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Um...]
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um para ele e um para mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.00,0:10:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.88,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Boa noite, Tanikaze{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.42,0:10:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Hoshijiro...]
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigada, Hoshijiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Parece delicioso.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hora de descobrir!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.07,0:10:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isso é ótimo!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Que bom ouvir isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Não consigo parar de comer!
