Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.76,0:10:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.80,0:11:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sugere uma estratégia cooperativa\Npara os vários esquadrões.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.89,0:11:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dá uma olhada.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.35,0:11:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Quem escreveu isso?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A irmã mais nova de Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aquela que você recomendou\Npara a escola de comando?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.86,0:11:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.69,0:11:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Ela possui um discernimento e uma mente estratégica excepcionais, capazes de me substituir.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.86,0:11:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Substituir você?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.78,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Você planeja ficar no campo de batalha, Seii?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Estamos sempre precisando de mais pilotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx100}...{\r}Agora, mais do que nunca—
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.06,0:11:32.54,DefaultAlt,,0,0,0,,Sou eu quem decide.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,e eu decido o que é melhor.{please leave this, im quoting gw bush}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.83,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu sei disso.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.25,0:11:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Diga-me se os\NGauna se moveram, em vez disso.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.76,0:11:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Conforme desejar.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.67,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele alterou sua trajetória e\Nestá indo direto para Sidônia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.05,0:11:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não acredito que possamos escapar dele.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:46.30,0:11:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Saíremos em dois dias.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.06,0:11:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dê aos militares de combate um dia de folga amanhã.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.23,0:11:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim, senhora!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.52,0:11:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Me mande a proposta de Midorikawa para eu ler.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.48,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigada.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.24,0:12:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Nossa...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,O que ele está fazendo com o Hoshijiro o tempo todo...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.22,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.89,0:12:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:29.89,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato[T0?]
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.31,0:12:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.98,0:12:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Quem é você?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.98,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Izana!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.90,0:12:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.36,0:12:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunato!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.28,0:12:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se dirija a mim com tamanha familiaridade!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.83,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Você sub-humano...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Shinatose{**-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.45,0:12:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Espera, Kunato!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Para com isso, Kunato{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.34,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que eles deram\NTsugumori para {\i1}ele{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanikaze[T0!]
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.06,0:13:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.31,0:13:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Graças aos céus.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.48,0:13:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Nenhum de vocês está seriamente ferido.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.03,0:13:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Devo estar chegando em breve.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.65,0:13:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuidem-se, os dois.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.03,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Obrigado!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.46,0:13:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu arruinei isso para você.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.88,0:13:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupe.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.09,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, certo!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver quem ganhou!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.01,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Akai Mochikuni é o vencedor.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.01,0:13:52.93,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,Sua sequência de vitórias continua.
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\blur0.8\pos(245,423.078)}m 0 0 l 221 0 221 54 0 54 {\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\blur0.8\pos(509,423.078)}m 0 0 l 221 0 221 54 0 54 {\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\blur0.8\pos(773,423.078)}m 0 0 l 221 0 221 54 0 54 {\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\p1\c&HFFFFFF&\blur0.8\pos(1037,423.078)}m 0 0 l 221 0 221 54 0 54 {\p0}
