Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Akai Mochikuni]
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Midorikawa Izumi]
Dialogue: 2,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.68,Sign,,0,0,0,,[T0Momose Hinata]
