Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.68,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,A competição em equipe foi\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx90}...{\r}vencida pelos seguintes pilotos...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.64,0:13:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Não estou surpreso que Akai{**-san} e os outros venceram!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.81,0:14:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eles são muito bons em equipe.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Os melhores de Sidônia?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.27,0:14:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uau!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.78,0:14:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pode entrar!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Olá.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Akai {**-san}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.28,0:14:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Entre.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpa estar te seguindo até o seu quarto, Tanikaze.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos para o mar amanhã.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Você quer vir com a gente?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nossa, Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.17,0:14:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,O mar!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.38,0:14:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode vir também.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Espera, sério?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos ver o mar! Não acredito nisso!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,O... mar?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tem um mar aqui em cima?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.86,0:14:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,O reservatório de água compreende um quarto de Sidonia.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.07,0:14:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um quarto? Isso é muita coisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:48.82,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Normalmente, só está aberto para pilotos experientes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindos ao reservatório.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.08,0:15:06.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HEE832C&\fnAveria Serif\b1\fs20\fax0.1\blur5\pos(582,97)\frz352}Batisfera Guiada por Heigus
Dialogue: 2,0:14:59.08,0:15:06.34,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HE7EB63&\fnAveria Serif\b1\fs20\fax0.1\blur0.5\pos(582,97)\frz352}Batisfera Guiada por Heigus
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.08,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado por nos convidar.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Não precisa ser tão formal.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu não sabia que este lugar existia.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.63,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Falando nisso,\Nsomos os únicos aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.22,0:15:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós reservamos o lugar\Npara o dia inteiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.89,0:15:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Para celebrar nossa vitória.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.20,0:15:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,É maravilhoso!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Olha, Nagate!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.79,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Havia espaço aqui\N{\alpha&HFF&\fscx80}...{\r}para Akai{**-san} e Momose{**-san} também...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apenas quatro pessoas são permitidas\Npor baúscópula, Nagate.{this was an actual submarine, but the name is so wonderfully bizarre im hoping we can reuse it}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.30,0:15:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixem-nos sozinhos por um tempo.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.26,0:15:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Pode ser o último encontro deles.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Desculpa, desculpa.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu só estava brincando.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.01,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,O que você quer dizer com "o último"?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gaunas do Outro Dia estão voltando.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele está vindo direto para nós.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.90,0:16:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fomos escolhidos para subjugar isso.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.19,0:16:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Não olhe para mim assim, Shinatose.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu estava brincando antes.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.49,0:16:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ele disse que te conhecer realmente\Najudou com o nervosismo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.95,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode ser capaz de lutar contra os Gauna,\Nmas não com o estômago vazio.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Ah, sim...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.42,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho certeza que podemos vencer os Gauna. Apenas nos observem.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.38,0:16:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Irmão{*Onii-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.97,0:16:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Você está realmente em um batiscafo\Ncom Tanikaze{**-san}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:38.26,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Yuhata...]
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Por que você não me convidou?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.85,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu odeio você, {*}Irmão{*Onii-chan}!{TL note: Brother means baka}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.73,0:16:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Você não está com medo, Akai{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.98,0:16:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nós vamos ficar bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.32,0:16:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,É um Gauna classe H2.\NNós não vamos perder.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.86,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho mais medo do seu pai\Ndo que dos Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nossa.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.58,0:17:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Espero que tudo isso acabe logo.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu também espero.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.94,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,O Esquadrão de Subjugação para os Gauna 487 partiu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Bom.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Entrem em formação e\Ninterceptem os Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.61,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Formação em quadrado!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:48.12,0:17:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Vinte segundos até a subjugação. A esquadra atinge o ponto de intercepção.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,10 segundos até a reversão do impulso.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}9...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}8...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.30,0:17:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}7...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}6...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}5...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.09,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}4...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.93,0:18:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}3...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.97,0:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}2...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}1...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.51,DefaultTop,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}{\i1}{*}Irmão{*Onii-chan}...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Reversão do impulso.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.85,0:18:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dez segundos até o contato inicial com G487 no ponto de intercepção projetado.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.23,0:18:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Distância: 300 quilômetros.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.02,0:18:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Iniciar operações ao avistar contato.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gauna à vista!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Siga as diretrizes e\Ndispersar sobre o alvo!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.99,0:18:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.24,0:18:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O Esquadrão de Subjugação engajou o G487.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.20,0:18:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Velocidade de combate estágio um,\Nengajando à média distância!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.71,0:18:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Canhões de partículas de Higgs autorizados.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fiquem atentos ao armazenamento de partículas.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.84,0:18:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.96,0:18:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Todas as unidades, atirem sem restrição.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.68,0:18:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Disparando o canhão Heigus!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.52,0:18:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Primeira salva, todos atingidos!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Os braços placentários foram seccionados!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.60,0:18:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki, Midorikawa, cerquem o alvo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Suprimam a regeneração placentária.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.23,0:18:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose, cubra minhas costas.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.11,0:19:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuidarei disso.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu o aniquilarei.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenho estibordo.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.58,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Disparando Canhão Heigus!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.08,0:19:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Estou pronto, Akai{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.76,0:19:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.51,0:19:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,O núcleo Gauna está exposto!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,O que houve?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pegou a Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.31,0:19:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Merda!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.23,0:19:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Deixa ela!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.85,0:19:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A regeneração está mais rápida do que o esperado!{The placenta is regenerating\Nfaster than anticipated!}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.94,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Cuidado, Akai!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.32,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[T0...[T1]Akai[T2]...]
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito, Momose.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.13,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Vermelho!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.01,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Vermelho!{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Vermelho{**-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.35,0:20:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Vermelho!{**-kun}! Vermelho!{**-kun}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:19.61,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Meu Deus...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Vermelho!{**-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{shikkari shiro}Escute-me!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.45,0:20:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,O vínculo ao quadro Akai foi cortado.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Os Gauna o pegaram.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Esquadrão de subjugação: Aoki assume o comando.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.37,0:20:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Perseguir G487.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.08,0:20:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx100}...{\r}Mas Momose—
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Não temos tempo.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.25,0:20:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignorem-na.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Você pode ir, Midorikawa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.67,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.01,0:20:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Segure no alvo um da saída.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentrem-se em conter os Gauna.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparem o Propulsor de Massa Pesada.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Propulsor de Massa Pesada sete, lado estibordo.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Abrindo o cano.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Eu vou carregar ele.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, exponha o núcleo para mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.32,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{Make sure there's nothing left\N}Seja minucioso, ou o\NKabizashi não conseguirá perfurá-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Copiado.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.45,0:21:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Disparando canhão de Higgs.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.04,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.25,0:21:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.17,0:21:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seu desgraçado!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.63,0:21:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Me devolva meu Akai{**-kun}!{so why do they let people like this become pilots again?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fique longe, Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Akai está morto!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{Heads up! }Braços Placentários!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.89,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{All frames, disperse!}Espalhem-se!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.32,0:21:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Escute-nos, Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.07,0:21:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.32,0:21:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fique aqui, Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Concentre-se na missão!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.24,0:21:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.99,0:21:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.67,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}Corra... Momose...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.30,0:22:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Estrutura de Midorikawa, danos graves.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Momose, parada cardiorrespiratória.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.39,0:22:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,O esquadrão de subjugação\Nhas foi aniquilado.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:21.65,0:22:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFF&\fscx60}...{\r}O esquadrão de Akai...
